org.eclipse.cdt.core.dom.ast
Interface IASTSimpleDeclaration

All Superinterfaces:
IASTAttributeOwner, IASTDeclaration, IASTNode
public interface IASTSimpleDeclaration
extends IASTDeclaration, IASTAttributeOwner

This is a simple declaration which contains a sequence of declSpecifiers followed by a list of declarators.
